onmental density. We show that this finding\nis incompatible with the predictions from hierarchical galaxy formation models,\nin which star formation is tightly linked to the assembly history of dark\nmatter halos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Feb 2002 21:06:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
